- All routes should be clearly defined with URLs matching page purposes.
- Authentication is required for all features; implement simple session-based login.
- Data read/write operations must be atomic to avoid corruption.
- Frontend must use the specified element IDs for consistency.
- Each programmer should focus on their assigned files only.
